modules.description: This module implements an MQTT client for connecting to an MQTT broker, publishing messages to topics, and subscribing to topics with specified quality of service (QoS) levels. It supports operations like connecting with optional TLS, credentials, and will messages, publishing messages with configurable QoS and retention, and subscribing to multiple topics. Concrete use cases include IoT device communication, real-time sensor data publishing, and event-driven messaging between distributed systems.
